a:17:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";s:11:"small_descr";s:215:"Confido belongs to a group of non-hormonal medicines that acts on the brain centers and male genitals. By acting on the brain centers Confido relieves agitations and anxiety and regulates the process of ejaculation.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:238:"Confido gehört zu der Gruppe von nichthormonalen Arzneimitteln, die auf die Gehirnzentren und männliche Genitalien wirken. Durch Einwirkung auf die Gehirnzentren lindert es Aufregungen und Ängste und regelt den Prozess der Ejakulation.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:264:"Confido est le membre du groupe de médicaments non hormonaux qui influencent ​​les centres cérébraux et les organes génitaux masculins. En influant les centres du cerveau Confido soulage l'anxiété et l'agitation et régule le processus de l'éjaculation.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:252:"Confido es un miembro del grupo de medicamentos non-hormonales que actúa sobre los centros cerebrales y los genitales masculinos. Al actuar sobre el  centros de cerebro Confido alivia la agitación y la ansiedad y regula el proceso de la eyaculación.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:236:"Confido appartiene ad un gruppo delle medicene non-ormonali che agiscono sul centro nervoso del cervello e genitali maschili. Agendo sul centro nervoso del cervello Confido leva agitazioni e ansia e regola il processo dell'eiaculazione.";s:10:"full_descr";s:950:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Confido is a non-hormonal and safe sexual stimulant.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>Take exactly as prescribed by your Health Provider.</p><p>If you miss a dose of this medicine and you are using it regularly, take it as soon as possible. Do not take 2 doses at once.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>1 tablet twice daily.</p><p><strong>STORAGE&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>The medication is contraindicated in known hypersensitivity to any of the medication ingredients.<br /><br />Talk with your doctor if you have any infectious diseases and hormonal disorders.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>The side effects of Confido include:</p><ul><li>skin rash</li><li>itching</li><li>burning</li><li>mood disorders (in very rare cases).</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:7:"21.3408";s:9:"pack_name";s:7:"bottles";s:4:"type";s:4:"caps";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:60;a:10:{i:5122;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5122";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"35.568";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5123;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5123";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"27.664";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5124;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5124";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"25.02933";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5125;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5125";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"23.712";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5126;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5126";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"22.9216";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5127;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5127";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.39467";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5128;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5128";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.01829";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5129;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5129";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"21.736";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5130;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5130";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"21.51644";s:4:"name";s:7:"Confido";}i:5131;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5131";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"21.3408"